{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":985,"text":"At Free America, we've done\na listening and learning tour."},{"time":4390,"text":"We visited not only with prosecutors"},{"time":7858,"text":"but with legislators,"},{"time":9628,"text":"with inmates in our state\nand local prisons."},{"time":15282,"text":"We've gone to immigration\ndetention centers."},{"time":18239,"text":"We've met a lot of people."},{"time":21174,"text":"And we've seen that redemption\nand transformation can happen"},{"time":27422,"text":"in our prisons, our jails\nand our immigration detention centers,"},{"time":32133,"text":"giving hope to those\nwho want to create a better life"},{"time":35174,"text":"after serving their time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":38028,"text":"Imagine if we also considered\nthe front end of this prison pipeline."},{"time":41964,"text":"What would it look like\nif we intervened,"},{"time":43929,"text":"with rehabilitation as a core value --"},{"time":46906,"text":"with love and compassion as core values?"},{"time":50523,"text":"We would have a society that is safer,"},{"time":52846,"text":"healthier"},{"time":54021,"text":"and worthy of raising our children in."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56864,"text":"I want to introduce you to James Cavitt."},{"time":60036,"text":"James served 12 years\nin the San Quentin State Prison"},{"time":64563,"text":"and is being released in 18 months."},{"time":67809,"text":"Now James, like you and me,"},{"time":69798,"text":"is more than the worst thing he's done."},{"time":73691,"text":"He is a father, a husband, a son, a poet."},{"time":77265,"text":"He committed a crime;"},{"time":78906,"text":"he's paying his debt,"},{"time":80547,"text":"and working hard to build the skills"},{"time":83035,"text":"to make the transition back\nto a productive life"},{"time":86762,"text":"when he enters the civilian\npopulation again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89807,"text":"Now James, like millions\nof people behind bars,"},{"time":92485,"text":"is an example of what happens"},{"time":94544,"text":"if we believe that our failings\ndon't define who we are,"},{"time":99019,"text":"that we are all worthy of redemption"},{"time":101345,"text":"and if we support those impacted\nby mass incarceration,"},{"time":105606,"text":"we can all heal together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":108034,"text":"I'd like to introduce you\nto James right now,"},{"time":110344,"text":"and he's going to share\nhis journey of redemption"},{"time":112852,"text":"through spoken word."}]},{"cues":[{"time":116432,"text":"James Cavitt: Thanks, John."},{"time":117806,"text":"TED, welcome to San Quentin."},{"time":120521,"text":"The talent is abundant\nbehind prison walls."},{"time":123608,"text":"Future software engineers,"},{"time":125664,"text":"entrepreneurs,"},{"time":126967,"text":"craftsmen,"},{"time":128142,"text":"musicians"},{"time":129317,"text":"and artists."},{"time":130624,"text":"This piece is inspired\nby all of the hard work"},{"time":133745,"text":"that men and women are doing on the inside"},{"time":136997,"text":"to create better lives\nand futures for themselves"},{"time":140346,"text":"after they serve their time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":142931,"text":"This piece is entitled, \"Where I Live.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":148218,"text":"I live in a world where most people\nare too afraid to go."},{"time":152441,"text":"Surrounded by tall, concrete walls,"},{"time":154801,"text":"steel bars,"},{"time":155976,"text":"where razor wire have a way"},{"time":157294,"text":"of cutting away at the hopes\nfor a brighter tomorrow."}]},{"cues":[{"time":161697,"text":"I live in a world"},{"time":162872,"text":"that kill people who kill people"},{"time":164429,"text":"in order to teach people"},{"time":165604,"text":"that killing people is wrong."},{"time":168285,"text":"Imagine that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":170111,"text":"Better yet,"},{"time":171286,"text":"imagine a world where healed people\nhelped hurt people heal"},{"time":174380,"text":"and become strong."},{"time":176427,"text":"Maybe then we would all\nbe singin' \"Redemption Song.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":181080,"text":"I live in a world that\nhas been called \"hell on Earth\""},{"time":184013,"text":"by those trapped inside."},{"time":187046,"text":"But I've come to the stark realization"},{"time":188993,"text":"that prison --"},{"time":190780,"text":"it really is what you make it."},{"time":193192,"text":"You see, in spite\nof the harshness of my reality,"},{"time":195931,"text":"there is a silver lining."},{"time":198470,"text":"I knew that my freedom was gonna come,"},{"time":200312,"text":"it was just a matter of time."},{"time":201725,"text":"And so I treated my first steps\nas if they were my last mile,"},{"time":205141,"text":"and I realized that you\ndon't have to be free"},{"time":208122,"text":"in order to experience freedom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":210890,"text":"And just because you're free,"},{"time":212673,"text":"doesn't mean that you have freedom."},{"time":214996,"text":"Many of us, for years,\nhave been battling our inner demons."},{"time":218266,"text":"We walk around smiling\nwhen inside we're really screamin':"},{"time":221631,"text":"freedom!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":224171,"text":"Don't you get it?"},{"time":226018,"text":"We're all serving time;"},{"time":227527,"text":"we're just in different places."},{"time":229780,"text":"As for me,"},{"time":230955,"text":"I choose to be free\nfrom the prisons I've created."},{"time":233559,"text":"The key:"},{"time":234734,"text":"forgiveness."},{"time":235909,"text":"Action's my witness."},{"time":237084,"text":"If we want freedom,"},{"time":239122,"text":"then we gotta think different."},{"time":241690,"text":"Because freedom ..."},{"time":245227,"text":"it isn't a place."},{"time":247783,"text":"It's a mind setting."}]},{"cues":[{"time":250996,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252171,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":255536,"text":"(Piano)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":273789,"text":"John Legend: Old pirates, yes, they rob I."},{"time":278233,"text":"Sold I to the merchant ships."},{"time":283414,"text":"Minutes after they took I"},{"time":287622,"text":"from the bottomless pit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":291191,"text":"My hands were made strong"},{"time":295969,"text":"by the hand of the almighty."},{"time":300213,"text":"We forward in this generation"},{"time":305798,"text":"triumphantly."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309343,"text":"Won't you help to sing"},{"time":314686,"text":"these songs of freedom?"},{"time":317899,"text":"'Cause all I ever had --"},{"time":323238,"text":"redemption songs."},{"time":327722,"text":"Redemption songs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":331947,"text":"Emancipate yourselves from mental slavery."},{"time":336277,"text":"None but ourselves can free our minds."},{"time":341253,"text":"Have no fear for atomic energy"},{"time":345269,"text":"'cause none of them can stop the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":349719,"text":"How long shall they kill our prophets"},{"time":353433,"text":"while we stand aside and look?"},{"time":358329,"text":"Some say it's just a part of it,"},{"time":362447,"text":"we've got to fulfill the book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366877,"text":"Won't you help to sing"},{"time":372048,"text":"these songs of freedom?"},{"time":375263,"text":"'Cause all I ever had --"},{"time":380322,"text":"redemption songs."},{"time":384387,"text":"Redemption songs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":386776,"text":"(Piano)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":404291,"text":"Emancipate yourselves from mental slavery."},{"time":408423,"text":"None but ourselves can free our minds."},{"time":412960,"text":"Have no fear for atomic energy"},{"time":417059,"text":"'cause none of them can stop the time."}]},{"cues":[{"time":420933,"text":"How long shall they kill our prophets"},{"time":425146,"text":"while we stand aside and look?"},{"time":428178,"text":"Some say it's just a part of it,"},{"time":433745,"text":"we've got to fulfill the book."}]},{"cues":[{"time":438151,"text":"Won't you help to sing"},{"time":443229,"text":"these songs of freedom?"},{"time":446418,"text":"'Cause all I ever had --"},{"time":451508,"text":"redemption songs."},{"time":455828,"text":"Redemption songs."},{"time":460071,"text":"These songs of freedom."}]},{"cues":[{"time":463428,"text":"'Cause all I ever had --"},{"time":468883,"text":"redemption songs."},{"time":473139,"text":"Redemption songs."},{"time":477695,"text":"Redemption songs."}]},{"cues":[{"time":485541,"text":"(Piano)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":487475,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":494081,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495584,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":496760,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}